    "fullHtml": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ko\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  <script>\n    tailwind.config = {\n      darkMode: 'class'\n    }\n  </script>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 p-4 transition-colors\">\n  <div class=\"space-y-8 pb-10\">\n    <!-- 1. 할 일 -->\n    <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">할 일</h3>\n        <span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">3</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">사용자 온보딩 완료</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10\">마케팅</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">내일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535711603863-10d97bc7a2d4?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" checked class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-400 line-through\">팀과 Dribbble 우선순위 문제 해결</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 1월 8일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" checked class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-400 line-through\">라이선스 변경 및 제품 제거</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10\">마케팅</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 2월 12일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599566150163-29194dcaad36?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 2. 진행 중 -->\n    <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">진행 중</h3>\n        <span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">4</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">진행 중(WIP) 대시보드</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">오늘</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">칸반 플로우 매니저</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-500/10\">템플릿</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 2월 12일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">제품 업데이트 - 2024년 4분기</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 2월 12일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">티켓 인박스 복귀 시 Figbot 댓글 자동화 설정</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 3월 8일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 3. 완료 -->\n    <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">완료</h3>\n        <span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">4</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">내부 피드백 관리</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">내일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">React Native 및 Flutter 프로젝트 진행</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-orange-600 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-500/10\">개발</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 1월 8일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">마케팅 에셋 디자인</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10\">마케팅</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 1월 8일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535711603863-10d97bc7a2d4?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#1A222C] p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /></svg>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"rounded border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 w-5 h-5\">\n          <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold flex-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">칸반 플로우 매니저</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-500/10\">템플릿</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500\">2027년 2월 12일</span>\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=100&h=100&fit=crop\" class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
